List Dataset

Source: R/jabr_list_dataset.R
jabr_list_dataset.Rd

List the dataset available at Open Data Jawa Barat.

jabr_list_dataset(update = FALSE)

Arguments

update

(logical) Whether to update the dataset list.

Value

A tibble.

Examples

# \donttest{
library(jabr)

jabr_list_dataset()
